Full Description: Good Day, My name is Joseph Sizemore; I am the Founder/CEO of Titan Automation Group, LLC. It would be an honor if you would allow me the opportunity to introduce myself and explain what we offer in the field of Industrial Automation and Integration.  Foremost, I am a follower of Christ. The company is designed around moral design, which comes with such a declaration. Without Christ, we are nothing. As the CEO of the company, it is my magnificent obsession to see your process, company, employees, and customers receive the highest level of service that can be offered in the industry. Titan is not only raising the bar in this industry we are redefining and redesigning the bar itself.  How are we doing that? Just to carry the title of Titan requires greater than five years of hands-on systems knowledge. Titans must be experts in a minimum of five separate applications with robotics and must have extensive PLC expertise. All of which a Titan is certified in by the original equipment manufacturer (OEM). Titans are truly the pinnacle of the industry! What does that mean to you and your company? It means that when you call Titan Group you get the best in the industry. Titans have paid their dues to this industry and have earned their title through overcoming unbelievable odds to accomplish their mission. Why would you choose Titan Group over any other company? As a company, we are young. We just got our Tax ID last year. However, the personnel in the company have decades of experience in multiple areas of automated manufacturing and process automation controls: We created the company as a means to not only care for our families but to actually bring people on who had our same values. We are tired of seeing large companies take smaller companies to the bank just to make a few extra dollars. Instead, we are better than the bigger companies and we care more because at the end of the day it is our families’ name that is on our work, not just Titan's. Other companies offer a body, one person who is versed either in one or maybe three of the required fields which you may need. We offer a one stop full integration service that is truly not just setting the bar but redefining the bar itself. Titan offers something that no other company in the world offers: a TITAN. Truly a professional expert who is driven by our core values. God First, Military Precision, and Deeply ingrained obsession. If you are going to do something, you cannot do anything except through Christ, Phil. 4:13. Organization Name: Platanides Through The Eye Of The Storm
Description: Author
Full Description: This book follows the life, experiences, and Christian Faith of a young boy born in Asia Minor in 1908; how he and his family managed to escape the Genocide of the Greek and Armenian Christians at the hands of Kemal Ataturk on September 13, 1922; their lives as refugees of genocide; how these events and events of World War II on the Island of Crete Greece affected them and their descendants; and the relationship between that boy, in his adult years, and his son, the author. The book deals with life’s storms that the boy and his son experienced and how their faith, in particular as practiced in their everyday lives, affected, and strengthened them so that they could move through the storms of life and emerge from the eye of those storms, remaining strong and committed in their Faith.  There is a stark comparison of life under the oppression of Muslim radicals seeking to eliminate Christianity; life under the control of the Nazi and Gestapo tyranny; and life under the Constitution of the United States where we are guaranteed freedom of religion, speech, choice, and the other rights granted Citizens of these United States of America.  The author warns future generations to not overlook the price paid for these freedoms; and that, if ignored, the suppression, tyranny and genocide that was suffered by our forefathers, which still exists in other parts of the world, can be experienced again by us, even here, in the United States of America.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Industry Groups: Content and Publishing, Media and Entertainment

Description: Esports for Everyone.
Full Description: eSports is a multiplayer video game played competitively for spectators, typically by professional gamers.  Professional gamers form an eSports team in order to compete with other eSports teams and battle for huge cash prizes in front of large audiences. eSports is lacking a “minor league” to foster everyday gamers that want to be a professional eSports gamer.  GameSlice.io is creating a minor league that allows anyone to enter and participate while using proprietary match making and skill trees to advance players through the ranks to ultimately compete in our pro-like, in-person finals for cash and prizes enabling professional teams to recruit players.
